.TH "locks_lock_inode_wait" 9 "locks_lock_inode_wait" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
locks_lock_inode_wait \- Apply a lock to an inode
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" locks_lock_inode_wait
.BI "(struct inode *inode "  ","
.BI "struct file_lock *fl "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "inode" 12
inode of the file to apply to
.IP "fl" 12
The lock to be applied
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Apply a POSIX or FLOCK style lock request to an inode.
